00:16:31,740 --> 00:16:34,243
- Kau cari pasal?
- Siapa yang mulakan?

270
00:16:34,326 --> 00:16:35,285
Betul juga.

271
00:16:48,632 --> 00:16:51,927
Ramai kata penyelidikan saya gagal,
saya tertekan

272
00:16:52,636 --> 00:16:55,139
