277
00:17:06,942 --> 00:17:08,861
Ini rekod tutup kedai terpantas.

278
00:17:08,944 --> 00:17:10,487
Mungkin sebab nama.

279
00:17:10,988 --> 00:17:12,948
Kenapa bangsawan buat piza?

280
00:17:13,449 --> 00:17:17,369
Pasti dapat sambutan
jika namanya Piza Vincenzo.

281
00:17:17,953 --> 00:17:19,121
Jahanam...

282
00:17:19,204 --> 00:17:22,499
Keesokan harinya, saya dipindahkan
ke bilik kecil.

283
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:24,710
Tapi saya amat bersyukur

284
00:17:25,210 --> 00:17:26,962
kerana bos kedai piza itu

285
00:17:27,046 --> 00:17:29,548
sentiasa biarkan TV terbuka ketika keluar.

286
00:17:29,631 --> 00:17:31,842
Dia buka saluran drama.

287
00:17:36,430 --> 00:17:38,932
Kepulangan aku disambut TV lagi.

288
00:17:39,016 --> 00:17:40,184
Dia kesunyian.

289
00:17:40,768 --> 00:17:42,603
Drama satu-satunya peneman dia.

