00:20:48,413 --> 00:20:49,748
Memang mengarut.

317
00:20:50,374 --> 00:20:51,833
Macam seluar kuning awak.

318
00:20:54,628 --> 00:20:55,754
Tapi memang benar.

319
00:20:56,255 --> 00:20:58,465
Saya dah laluinya sendiri.

320
00:21:00,217 --> 00:21:02,052
Nuget ayam, beluncas,

321
00:21:02,135 --> 00:21:03,011
burung zombi.

